Privacy Policy for Luca
Welcome to Luca, powered by Lemonilab FZCO, Dubai. Your financial assistant app. We are committed to safeguarding your personal information and respecting your privacy rights. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data when you use our application and explains your privacy rights and legal protections.
What Data Do We Collect?
Uploaded Data: Luca collects invoices you upload.
Extracted Data: We automatically extract information from these invoices to generate reports.
How Do We Use Your Data?
We use your data for the following purposes:
Organize and Generate Reports: Your data is used to create organized and useful reports.
Improve Application Performance: We analyze data to enhance the application's performance and user experience.
Data Use Assurance
We do not use your data for advertising purposes, and we do not directly target users using their personal information or data extracted from their invoices.
Storage and Security
Uploaded invoices are securely stored. We employ advanced security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, modification,or deletion.
Data Retention
We retain your uploaded invoices and extracted data for as long as necessary for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
Your Privacy Rights
Access:
You have the right to request copies of your personal data.
Correction:
You can request the correction of any inaccurate information.
Erasure:
You can request the erasure of your personal data.
Objection:
You have the right to object to our processing of your personal data.
Advertising and Data Use Assurance
At Luca, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your data is used responsibly. We want to assure you that:
We do not use your data for advertising purposes.
We do not share your data with third parties for advertising purposes.
Our primary focus is to provide you with a secure and efficient platform for managing your financial data. You can trust that your data will be handled with the utmost care and in accordance with our Privacy Policy.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy periodically. Please review this page regularly for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
